I am creating an AI agent using Gemini model. I already configured the API key in the Google colab. Now I would like to import the key in my code Objective: I would like to import the api key in my code. So I can call the Gemini API in my code to get the response for a user prompt. Style: python code compatible for jupyter notebook Tone: Easy to understand for new AI Agent developer Audience: New AI Agent Developer with limited knowledge of AI Response: It should respond the python code for importing API Keys to the code.
